370
00:24:08,238 --> 00:24:09,531
Shall I just say it?

371
00:24:11,241 --> 00:24:14,995
I'm being considerate to you,
so please choose.

372
00:24:15,871 --> 00:24:18,874
Noh Hwa-young, you're just so…

373
00:24:21,334 --> 00:24:23,211
Go wait outside, Vice Corps Commander.

374
00:24:23,295 --> 00:24:25,172
-Minister…
-Get out!

375
00:24:38,268 --> 00:24:40,020
