381
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:06,338
This is the most considerate thing
I can do for you.

382
00:25:06,838 --> 00:25:08,632
I cannot resign as

383
00:25:08,715 --> 00:25:10,926
the Division Commander
for something like this.

384
00:25:11,009 --> 00:25:12,344
What?

385
00:25:12,427 --> 00:25:14,471
"For something like this"?

386
00:25:14,554 --> 00:25:17,849
