395
00:25:36,868 --> 00:25:37,994
What?

396
00:25:38,578 --> 00:25:41,248
You've gone totally mad
because of your son!

397
00:25:41,748 --> 00:25:45,001
You've finally shown
your filthy true colors to me!

398
00:25:45,669 --> 00:25:47,254
I'll hear no more.

399
00:25:47,337 --> 00:25:48,421
You!

400
00:25:48,505 --> 00:25:50,298
You'll be dishonorably discharged soon!

401
00:25:51,549 --> 00:25:54,094
