402
00:26:01,685 --> 00:26:04,145
I carried out your order perfectly.

403
00:26:04,229 --> 00:26:07,649
I told you to find ways to make
that investigator couple understand!

404
00:26:07,732 --> 00:26:09,901
I didn't tell you to kill them, you jerk!

405
00:26:09,985 --> 00:26:13,488
Cutting off any potential problems
at the root is the way I found.

406
00:26:13,571 --> 00:26:16,533
That's the only way
to prevent further trouble.

407
00:26:16,616 --> 00:26:18,910
Are you nuts? You idiot!

408
00:26:18,994 --> 00:26:20,829
Colonel, you must now…

409
00:26:21,913 --> 00:26:24,082
Be on my side

410
00:26:24,749 --> 00:26:27,961
until the end,
as long as I remain in the military.

411
00:26:29,045 --> 00:26:31,006
That was what I said.

412
00:26:31,089 --> 00:26:32,173
You…

413
00:26:33,133 --> 00:26:34,759
How dare you…

414
00:26:35,969 --> 00:26:37,178
How could you!

415
00:26:38,388 --> 00:26:40,932
