416
00:26:41,516 --> 00:26:45,312
Which means this recording
is just the tip of the iceberg.

417
00:26:46,313 --> 00:26:47,397
Hey!

418
00:26:48,189 --> 00:26:52,610
Are you even aware
that this can destroy you too?

419
00:26:52,694 --> 00:26:54,112
There's no battle you can win

420
00:26:54,195 --> 00:26:56,239
without getting your hands
covered in blood.

421
00:26:57,115 --> 00:27:00,285
All wars require blood to win.

422
00:27:02,370 --> 00:27:04,581
I was always ready
to have a puddle of blood

423
00:27:04,664 --> 00:27:06,750
under my feet

424
00:27:06,833 --> 00:27:09,669
in order for me to get up to

425
00:27:09,753 --> 00:27:11,838
a higher place.

426
00:27:13,131 --> 00:27:16,718
Because this is the world of men

427
00:27:16,801 --> 00:27:19,179
who are scared
to have their hands covered in blood.

428
00:27:22,766 --> 00:27:23,850
So…

429
00:27:24,559 --> 00:27:27,270
if you want to stay
in that position longer,

430
00:27:27,771 --> 00:27:29,856
take care of this case immediately.

431
00:27:31,983 --> 00:27:34,361
From this moment on,
I give you orders, Minister.

432
00:27:43,536 --> 00:27:44,579
Salute!

433
00:27:44,662 --> 00:27:45,663
Go on.

434
00:27:51,002 --> 00:27:52,504
What happened, Minister?

435
00:27:58,301 --> 00:28:00,220
CHIEF MILITARY PROSECUTOR SEO JOO-HYUK

436
00:28:01,554 --> 00:28:03,598
Prosecutor Doh, come to my office.

437
00:28:03,681 --> 00:28:06,476
How's the investigation
on the mass shooting going?

438
00:28:06,559 --> 00:28:08,812
Pyeon Sang-ho admitted
to all of his crimes,

439
00:28:08,895 --> 00:28:10,146
and based on the survivors,

440
00:28:10,230 --> 00:28:12,774
we figured out how it was carried out.

441
00:28:12,857 --> 00:28:14,943
There should be the cause of the accident?

442
00:28:15,026 --> 00:28:16,986
We're looking
into the possibility of abuse.

443
00:28:18,571 --> 00:28:21,116
I read the testimonies
of the surviving soldiers.

444
00:28:21,199 --> 00:28:24,035
But you must look into it
a bit further than this!

445
00:28:24,119 --> 00:28:26,287
You're the military prosecutors
of Seo Joo-hyuk!

446
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,919
No parent would want to

447
00:28:33,002 --> 00:28:35,964
send their kids to the military
when things like this happen!

448
00:28:36,047 --> 00:28:37,590
Back in my day,

449
00:28:37,674 --> 00:28:40,093
when a mass shooting like this occurred,

450
00:28:40,176 --> 00:28:42,387
they tried to cover up the case

451
00:28:42,470 --> 00:28:45,181
and made people even angrier!

452
00:28:45,682 --> 00:28:48,893
We, the military prosecutors,
must keep calm

453
00:28:48,977 --> 00:28:52,897
and figure out the truth more accurately
for cases like this!

454
00:28:52,981 --> 00:28:56,526
That was what we did back in my day!
So you guys should do the same!

455
00:28:57,235 --> 00:28:59,612
-Get it?
-Yes, Staff Judge Advocate.

456
00:28:59,696 --> 00:29:00,947
Yes, sir.

457
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:03,366
Soon-to-be Lieutenant Colonel.

458
00:29:03,950 --> 00:29:04,784
Salute!

459
00:29:06,453 --> 00:29:07,287
Salute!

460
00:29:09,122 --> 00:29:10,874
-You can go now.
-Yes, sir.

461
00:29:12,459 --> 00:29:13,877
Let's go get some latte, Cha.

462
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,879
