to a scene of a mass shooting.

465
00:29:24,763 --> 00:29:26,014
What was it like?

466
00:29:27,515 --> 00:29:30,393
I saw how a war truly is with my own eyes.

467
00:29:30,477 --> 00:29:32,937
It was simply horrendous.

468
00:29:33,980 --> 00:29:37,192
Private First Class Pyeon
isn't telling his motive at all,

469
00:29:37,275 --> 00:29:39,486
so it'll be hard
for our two military prosecutors

470
00:29:39,569 --> 00:29:40,904
to request the sentencing.

471
00:29:41,488 --> 00:29:45,158
Prosecutor Doh will find out
if there was cruelty or not.

472
00:29:45,658 --> 00:29:49,037
You know, like how the doctors
can diagnose immediately

473
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:51,122
by looking at an X-ray photo.

474
00:29:51,206 --> 00:29:53,625
