military prosecutors.

475
00:29:53,708 --> 00:29:55,543
What's Prosecutor Doh's specialty?

476
00:29:55,627 --> 00:29:57,378
-His hunch.
-His hunch…

477
00:29:57,462 --> 00:29:59,756
